as and energy trading space in houston and calgary he received his ms in accounting from the university of virginia and a ba in english and economics at rice university publications cover the policy tightrope in gas producing countries stimulating domestic demand without discouraging supply mark c thurber joe chang program on energy and sustainable development 2011 pdf+ events & presentations energy working group china's shifting priorities and 12th five year plan january 12 2011 research presentation joe chang search people everything recent commentary pesd paper helps frame conference session on asian natural gas june 6 2011 announcement support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
